+### 命令行工具
+
+#### top命令
+
+```
+Processes: 411 total, 5 running, 406 sleeping, 2126 threads                      15:12:53
+Load Avg: 3.24, 3.04, 3.10  CPU usage: 18.22% user, 6.71% sys, 75.5% idle
