+
+PID   COMMAND      %CPU  TIME     #TH    #WQ  #PORT MEM    PURG   CMPR PGRP PPID STATE
+637   webstorm     2.0   02:49.89 60     3    354   665M   64K    0B   637  1    sleeping
+5033  lldb-rpc-ser 0.0   00:10.29 8      1    69    625M   0B     0B   5033 1228 sleeping
